sentences: Kelly Keeling was born on June 25, 1966, and is an American musician and songwriter.
Kelly formed the band Balance in 2012 with guitarist/co- writer Kim Roy, (formerly of the band Kingdom), and reunited Baton Rouge for a new recording on Frontier Records, which was cancelled in 2013.

In June 2021, police in Scott, Louisiana, a city located in Lafayette Parish, obtained a warrant for Kelly Keeling for negligent homicide in connection with the suspicious death of 40-year-old Michael Hebert, a Lafayette Parish resident.
Keeling's whereabouts were still unknown as of early July, 2021.
